2026-05-15T18:48:54.3237899Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3238716Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3239390Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3240084Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3240877Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3302208Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3303021Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T18:48:54.3303692Z 233            preserve via tools:node="merge".
